GeigerTracker is a project to create web-based graphs of radiation data
collected from a geiger counter. This is the server, written in PHP with a
MySQL database.

NOTE: This project isn't done yet.

To install:
- Download the source code, extract it into a folder on your webserver
- Create a new MySQL database, username, and password
- Copy config-sample.php into config.php
- Edit config.php and add your MySQL info and a random secret (the same 
  secret your client uses)
- Go to your website for the first time to install the database

You can find the server here:
https://github.com/micahflee/geigertracker_server

You can find the client here:
https://github.com/micahflee/geigertracker_client
